{"tid":926161,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"銀河英雄傳說悶唔悶 ?","createTime":"2018-12-03T08:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T04:32:44.000Z","uid":70760,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"00382ca1b64d15aa322f9925492b82325686bfe8","tid":926161,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:57:57.000Z","msg":"準備入坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0190ad636562d6b50971c144c58bef192581c28","tid":926161,"uid":159746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:33:13.000Z","msg":"期待智鬥應該會失望<br />\n利申:淨係睇過新版同小說"},{"pid":"ca1e2e5572fae178c73810b4770f12047585eb46","tid":926161,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:35:02.000Z","msg":"唔好睇新版"},{"pid":"dbf5125bef578f93a0fc03cf1da45f369f7a7289","tid":926161,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:37:40.000Z","msg":"唔撚鐘意講經咪覺悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065c82548bdbcb72e42da6d879b14c87ebbba9e8","tid":926161,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:37:48.000Z","msg":"中學睇過幾本小說<br />\n印象中唔悶"},{"pid":"eacbe10c9e2170e8ac21a6fa913bff5c9d4ee43a","tid":926161,"uid":33798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:39:52.000Z","msg":"如果覺得睇書會悶可以睇舊版OVA<br />\n整體係好好睇<br />\n就算悶都值得睇哂"},{"pid":"5c4c24f44170a337964e755f01c0b19f31e06f03","tid":926161,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:44:07.000Z","msg":"唔悶，好撚好睇，神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef2914fe40f12b3a048eca0f1b9d1ab195eb515","tid":926161,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T22:52:10.000Z","msg":"覺得悶嘅人係因為佢唔成熟"},{"pid":"bfaab9641699bad273eaab32f0076c9e8095ba72","tid":926161,"uid":90259,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:46:35.000Z","msg":"田中芳樹會笑鳩晒所有政治思想同意識形態，你接受唔到「正確」立場俾田中借角色把口嘲諷會覺得好悶<br />\n唔覺得呢啲嘢好睇亦都會覺得悶<br />\n人物好有性格，但佢地碰撞嘅火花多數係來自價值觀嘅不同，所以唔鍾意/理解田中戲謔式寫作會覺得啲角色好似好on9<br />\n「點解邊個唔做乜乜物物」「明知會點點點都要咁咁咁」<br />\n所謂鬥智部分唔算出色，宇宙艦隊戰描寫有乜野不足俾人講到爛<br />\n<br />\n你唔鍾意睇其實唔代表乜嘢，就係唔啱睇咁簡單<br />\n鍾意睇更加唔代表乜嘢"},{"pid":"cff11479b66cab118ff117123a93896a2a5d0067","tid":926161,"uid":2654,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T20:38:04.000Z","msg":"如果你對政治有興趣想入門一定啱睇 我本身讀政治 我睇完覺得其實睇呢本野去理解乜叫民主應該快過你上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為民主主義乾杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你對歷史係當故仔睇咁你更加要去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特別呢本野應該係少有用領導人 將領角度而可以放係動漫台討論既書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢本野每個有人名既角色都幾乎校級以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過鬥智方面...我諗田中都係普通人所以諗唔出乜神奇妙計...當時又冇wows Stellaris之類所以田中係用陸戰去寫宇宙戰所以...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後楊元帥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef64b7b768a5f6acb8626e8bea6b2af9764747d","tid":926161,"uid":40450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T05:12:59.000Z","msg":"小說我年年都重睇一次<br />\n睇幾多次都唔覺悶"},{"pid":"29957c8ad9e0618dea047e78227fbf74eaec72fb","tid":926161,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"悶就唔會悶既，可以慢慢嘆<br />\n我自己就覺得佢精彩過亞爾斯蘭戰記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1eeb58a158575d2e37c5b46c238bfc6ecc840e","tid":926161,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:10:57.000Z","msg":"入門級政治小說，難得 d 野好貼地，<br />\n同而家香港差唔多。<br />\n<br />\n以前細個時覺得好睇，而家更加佩服田中芳可以將 d 曆久常新既野整理得咁好睇同咁貼地。"},